{"type": "article", "id": 13898, "title": "创意家居产品", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-24T08:03:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000250SNA14cskvWlpEefK.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是来自 Bina Baitel Studio 设计工作室的一套创意家居产品，其中一款是一个和挂毯连接在一起的床头柜，另外一款式一个和地毯连接在一起的双床头柜。绿色的“瀑布”从床头柜上流出，进入用户的房间，像是开了一扇窗，进入另外的一片风光。尽管这个配色实在是让人想吐槽太过于焦虑，但是从创意来看，或许会有所启发。<a href=\"http://www.binabaitel.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看工作室其他作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141552U4mJo6753LdCESWc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.47916667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141553r6fJ0tbsFoeAMVim.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141553nQeSXghqfLklJcUV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69479167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141554WPbtf6DgkJzLTncr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60208333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}